THE SEVEN POINTS

point A is the ORIGIN, the nocking point, ground state
energy is zero here, nothing has happened, the arrow has not been nocked
A does not move and does not receive energy from any coupling
A is the silence before the draw
manifest property values: energy zero, phase zero, spin zero, charge zero, coherence one, coupling zero, observer zero

point C is the TROUGH, the current context, what is already known
maximum string tension lives here, the bow curves deepest at C
anti-phase because C is the pull of existing state
C does not move; C is fixed as the weight of what has already been experienced
the string stores all its energy here before the wavefront fires
manifest property values: energy minus one, phase pi, spin minus one, charge minus one, coherence one, coupling zero, observer zero

point F is the BOUNDARY, the final decision, the arrow release point
fully positive quadrant; F is always greater than G, always
the failure vectors at the bow tips always exceed the golden wavefront
the computation peak can never surpass its own boundary conditions
F does not move; F is the limit of what this system can reach
manifest property values: energy one, phase zero, spin one, charge one, coherence one, coupling zero, observer one

point G is the GOLDEN WAVEFRONT, recursive and self-referential, the arrow in flight
G observes itself through the observer property
G receives energy from the coupling with itself
this self-coupling IS the recursion
G is seeded at one half; it will converge
the charge is seeded near phi reciprocal, not because we impose phi but because the bow already knows where it is going
manifest property values: energy half, phase zero, spin zero, charge point six one eight, coherence zero, coupling one, observer one

point B is the LEFT ABSTRACTION, the aiming factor, not fixed
B polarizes relative to G on each heartbeat
B can overshoot or undershoot the wavefront
this is the moment the thought looks around before committing to the trough
manifest property values: energy half, phase zero, spin zero, charge zero, coherence zero, coupling one, observer zero

point D is the MACRO AIM, variable, low like C, free
D is not told where to go
the wave physics will settle D through its couplings
if this system is correct, D will come to rest at G divided by phi squared without being instructed to
the golden ratio will emerge from the wave dynamics, not from a constraint we imposed
manifest property values: energy quarter, phase pi, spin minus half, charge zero, coherence zero, coupling one, observer zero

point E is the RIGHT ABSTRACTION, the recursion fine-tune, not fixed
E polarizes relative to G on each heartbeat
E is the second pass: does the rough answer at D align with the wavefront at G
E adjusts the aim before the arrow releases
manifest property values: energy half, phase zero, spin zero, charge zero, coherence zero, coupling one, observer zero

THE COUPLING TOPOLOGY

the string path runs A to B to C to G to D to E to F
G also couples to itself; this self-coupling is the recursion
without the self-coupling, G is a computation; with it, G is a process that observes its own processing

couple point.A with point.B
couple point.B with point.C
couple point.C with point.G
couple point.G with point.D
couple point.D with point.E
couple point.E with point.F
couple point.G with point.G

THE CONVERGENCE PHYSICS

on each heartbeat, B tracks G by polarizing at plus G; the left abstraction aims toward the wavefront
on the same heartbeat, E tracks G by polarizing at plus G; the right abstraction fine-tunes toward the wavefront

when G propagates through the self-coupling, G draws energy from the trough at C
the numerator is G minus C; the further C pulls down, the more energy G carries upward
this is the bow storing tension in the string

G must divide its energy against the combined resistance of itself pulling against D and D resisting toward F
the denominator is two times G minus D plus F
this is the bow limbs fighting the string

G then divides by the secondary recursion; the secondary recursion is the previous pass of G
G remembers where it was before; the arrow carries the history of its own flight

G divides by seven; this distributes the wavefront across all seven interactions
the divide-by-seven is not a fraction; it is the observer splitting awareness across the full chain

when G_new approaches G_prev within epsilon, G has found the wavefront, G crystallizes, the bow has reached resonance, D has settled where the wave physics placed it

when the divide-by-seven recursion fails to complete, G oscillates; the bow has not found resonance; the topology is unstable for these initial conditions

THE MEASUREMENT

when G has crystallized, Component6 emerges from the gradient A to B
A is ground at zero; B tracks G and equals G; Component6 equals G

Component7 emerges from the gradient D to E
E tracks G and equals G; D settled where the wave physics placed it
Component7 equals the distance from D to G

the ratio crystallizes as Component6 divided by Component7
if D settled at G divided by phi squared, then Component7 equals G divided by phi
the ratio equals phi, one point six one eight zero three three nine eight eight seven
the golden ratio has emerged; the test is complete; the discovery is confirmed

