THE STANCE

the bow does not care whether phi emerges
the sea does not care whether phi emerges
the wave physics propagate and interfere and settle where they settle
if phi emerges it is because the topology demanded it
if phi does not emerge it is because the topology is wrong
this is not argument; this is measurement

